    "mitreControlType": "DETECTION",
    "mitreControlDescription": "Monitor DLL/PE file events, specifically creation of these binary files as well as the loading of DLLs into processes. Look for DLLs that are not recognized or not normally loaded into a process.\n \n Note: This looks for unsigned images that may be loaded by regsvr32, while attempting to eliminate false positives stemming from Windows/Program Files binaries.\n \n Analytic 5 - Loading Unsigned Images \n \n <code>(source=\"*WinEventLog:Microsoft-Windows-Sysmon/Operational\" EventCode=\"7\") (Image=\"C:\\\\Windows\\\\System32\\\\regsvr32.exe\" OR Image=\"C:\\\\Windows\\\\SysWOW64\\\\regsvr32.exe\") Signed=false ImageLoaded!=\"C:\\\\Program Files*\" ImageLoaded!=\"C:\\\\Windows\\\\*\"|stats values(ComputerName) as \"Computer Name\" count(ImageLoaded) as ImageLoadedCount by ImageLoaded</code>",
