    "mitreControlDescription": "Monitor for COM objects loading DLLs and other modules not typically associated with the application.(Citation: Enigma Outlook DCOM Lateral Movement Nov 2017)\n \n Note: Sysmon Event ID 7 (Image loaded) can be used to monitor for suspicious DLLs loaded by the DCOM Server Process Launcher which runs inside of svchost.exe. This is a particularly noisy event and can generate a large volume of data, so we recommend baselining and filtering out any known benign svchost.exe module loads that occur as part of its typical operation.",
