    "mitreControlType": "DETECTION",
    "mitreControlDescription": "Monitor for loading and/or execution of artifacts associated with PowerShell specific assemblies, such as System.Management.Automation.dll (especially to unusual process names/locations).(Citation: Sixdub PowerPick Jan 2016)(Citation: SilentBreak Offensive PS Dec 2015)\n \n Analytic 1 - Processes loading PowerShell assemblies\n \n <code>source=\"*WinEventLog:Microsoft-Windows-Sysmon/Operational\" EventCode=\"7\" | where ModulePath LIKE \"%system.management.automation%\" OR\n  FileDescription LIKE \"%system.management.automation%\"</code>",
